{"tid":160712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑客預告日內陸續有】再有荷李活女星遭流出艷照 辛潘女、露絲中招","createTime":"2017-03-18T03:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T09:46:48.000Z","uid":20419,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d32f7485806139accd1ba95902ff936dd768e79","tid":160712,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170318&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56445090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170318%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56445090&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=51a9afaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170318%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56445090&h=da5b75dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170318&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56445090</a> 【黑客預告日內陸續有】再有荷李活女星遭流出艷照 辛潘女、露絲中招"},{"pid":"f2459fe7857dec179e7308d6c34fffa19ef4a2d7","tid":160712,"uid":19979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"Seed呢"},{"pid":"63462a999b53651a03f5d9019df4681cd1f63ad1","tid":160712,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"Seed呢"},{"pid":"6a83b98a6f6edac4854a02c3608f6fb9996ad6c8","tid":160712,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a078093ce0bf1fa29cc1d5f15da3ce91a4fba9","tid":160712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"【黑客預告日內陸續有】再有荷李活女星遭流出艷照 辛潘女、露絲中招<br />\n<br />\n即時娛樂  2017-03-18 11:06:49 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489805378_33ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489805378_33ce.jpg&h=d9264d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於流出的艷照中，露絲三點全裸自拍及自慰。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489805381_1863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489805381_1863.jpg&h=03274f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辛潘女兒Dylan的私密照中有她露出胸部對鏡自拍及疑似自慰片段。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489805382_385b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489805382_385b.jpg&h=4680559d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《綠箭俠》女星Katie被流出與男子口交的照片。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489805384_6b0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489805384_6b0f.jpg&h=f7d97b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摔角手Paige於twitter就事件回應，寫到:「我個人及私密照片被盜，沒有經我同意流出。」<br />\n荷李活再發生女星遭黑客盜取私密照事件，繼英國女星愛瑪屈臣（Emma Watson），以及正懷孕嘅《賤熊2》（Ted2）女星雅曼達施菲（Amanda Seyfried）嘅試衫照及裸照分別流出後，今日有更多女星成為受害人，包括荷李活片《索女．喪屍．機關槍》（Planet Terror）女主角露絲麥高雲（Rose McGowan）、影星辛潘（Sean Penn）女兒Dylan Penn、《綠箭俠》（Arrow）女星Katie Cassidy及靚女摔角手Paige等，每人約有十多張，而且當中不乏清楚見到樣子。<br />\n<br />\n流出的艷照中，包括有露絲麥高雲三點全裸自拍及自慰照，亦有疑似其性愛片段。辛潘女兒的私密照中，有她露出胸部對鏡自拍，以及照太陽燈時全裸自拍，及疑似自慰片段；至於Katie的照片中，則有與一男子口交。摔角手Paige於twitter就事件回應，寫到：「我個人及私密照片被盜，沒有經我同意流出。」<br />\n<br />\n黑客於論壇中揚言，未來數日會有更加多女星裸照流出，如真人騷女星Kylie Jenner、影星瑪麗莎托梅（Marisa Tomei）及影后珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）。<br />\n<br />\n早於2014年便有黑客入侵荷李活女星嘅雲端檔案，盜取私密照，當時涉及的女星多達100名。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》第十二屆金話梅電影選舉（Golden Plum）又嚟喇!由今日起，請在以下網址（ <a href=\"http://campaign.appledaily.com/goldenplum2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.appledaily.com%2Fgoldenplum2017&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=55caafe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.appledaily.com%2Fgoldenplum2017&h=0fa9e6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://campaign.appledaily.com/goldenplum2017</a> ）投票，選出心目中的爛片之霸，截止日期係4月6日，賽果將於香港電影金像獎舉行前夕（4月8日）揭曉。"},{"pid":"c5bce63d025f756f29362d52222e4016bbada99a","tid":160712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6178bb58498e65fdac3613063145988dfa8a94d","tid":160712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7490c4e555e543fda2f70b31d4dcf4902fa5dbd","tid":160712,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"咪又係女人"},{"pid":"5a586e5c5a33929453c4c88ac2884272ca929eca","tid":160712,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"圖呀！"},{"pid":"f6bc161df82e2dbdf69200dfe0aafe60cadcdc95","tid":160712,"uid":63187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"圖呀"},{"pid":"53a93c584150b44108b583a2bfd1566d50823ada","tid":160712,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"次次都無連登份"},{"pid":"5507e672a2b8164ff308d3e072c8807a7f14ced0","tid":160712,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"點解arrow咁多女要係最唔靚嗰個有流出"},{"pid":"c30698ae0cf62352c7445ae31beafead46370c08","tid":160712,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"想問下hack到入Emma Watson個account未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a79e9d6fbf1cb6210da89642f61c786b9903ac4","tid":160712,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"外國版艷照事件。"}